        "subject": "LU-1623 Atomically update server export connection flags",
        "message": "LU-1623 Atomically update server export connection flags\n\nIt appears that we update export connection flags on MDS in two step.\nStep one is simple feature matching and then much later we also\nremove various security-related bits as needed.\nIn the case of reconnect some requestp processing can see interim\nstate of the flags and assuem client has capabilities that it does\nnot really have and send some confusing replies to it.\n\nThis patch moves all exp_vonnection_flags assignment in mdt to\nmdt_init_sec_level only.\n\nChange-Id: I3a6b16a589083feeb4ab166625648cd7a1652793\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
  },
